      "side": 1,
      "message": "given in Soong you have 0-3 and g, these should correspond to that. If you\u0027re representing `g` as explicitly passing `g` that would make sense, but an empty string as the default input seems reasonable -- I\u0027d just aim for consistency between Soong and Bazel when `CLANG_DEFAULT_DEBUG_LEVEL` is not set.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 519,
