    },
    {
      "unresolved": true,
      "key": {
        "uuid": "dd3c4ee6_c9b8f2de",
        "filename": "BUILD.bazel",
        "patchSetId": 4
      },
      "lineNbr": 536,
      "author": {
        "id": 1687194
      },
      "writtenOn": "2023-07-10T19:51:41Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Then, you\u0027d need to pass it to the toolchain as an input.\n\nYou can access the `BuildSettingInfo` as you\u0027re doing, but given that in Soong, you\u0027re expecting 0-3, I\u0027d recommend adding `-g` as a prefix. If you do this, you can drop the `config_setting`\n\nAlternatively, you can keep the `config_setting`, but you need config_setting per debug level:\n\ni.e.\n\n```\nconfig_setting(\n      name \u003d \"clang_default_debug_level_0\",\n      flag_values \u003d {\n          \":clang_default_debug_level\": \"0\"\n      },\n)\n\nconfig_setting(\n      name \u003d \"clang_default_debug_level_1\",\n      flag_values \u003d {\n          \":clang_default_debug_level\": \"1\"\n      },\n)\n...\n```\n\n```\n    debug_flag \u003d select({\n        \"//prebuilts/clang/host/linux-x86:clang_default_debug_level_0\": \"-g0\",\n        \"//prebuilts/clang/host/linux-x86:clang_default_debug_level_1\": \"-g1\",\n        \"//prebuilts/clang/host/linux-x86:clang_default_debug_level_2\": \"-g2\",\n        \"//prebuilts/clang/host/linux-x86:clang_default_debug_level_3\": \"-g3\",\n        \"//conditions:default\": \"-g\",\n    })\n    common_toolchain_config \u003d dict(\n        [\n            (\"target_os\", target_os),\n            (\"target_arch\", target_arch),\n            (\"clang_version\", clang_version),\n            (\"libclang_rt_builtin\", libclang_rt_path),\n            (\"libclang_rt_ubsan_minimal\", libclang_rt_ubsan_minimal_path),\n            (\"target_flags\", target_flags),\n            (\"compiler_flags\", compiler_flags),\n            (\"linker_flags\", linker_flags),\n            (\"rtti_toggle\", rtti_toggle),\n            (\"debug_flag\", debug_flag),\n        ],\n    )\n```\n\nand you\u0027d need to thread this through.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 527,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 536,
        "endChar": 1
      },
      "revId": "ee28c8f1e305ab4af080751801c1dd9ddf119b20",
      "serverId": "85c56323-6fa9-3386-8a01-6480fb634889"
    },
